{
  "texts": [
    "Notably, terms like \"breast cancer,\" \"breast neoplasm,\" \"machine learning,\" and \"deep learning\" have exhibited more dynamic growth compared to others.",
    "For example, the cumulative occurrence of the top 10 keywords includes \"mammography\" (6), \"female\" (3), \"artificial intelligence\" (2), \"human\" (1), \"breast cancer\" (2), \"machine learning\" (0), \"humans\" (2), \"article\" (1), \"deep learning\" (0), and \"breast neoplasms\" (2).",
    "In contrast, by 2024, the keywords with the highest increase in occurrences from 2000 to 2024 were \"mammography\" (3171), \"female\" (1739), \"artificial intelligence\" (1691), \"human\" (1483), \"breast cancer\" (1444), \"machine learning\" (1062), \"humans\" (1012), \"article\" (973), \"deep learning\" (892), and \"breast neoplasms\" (790).",
    "Furthermore, we analysed the co-occurrence of authors' keywords using biblioshiny.",
    "The co-occurrence network helps understand the thematic areas covered within the research field and identify the most critical and current issues."
  ]
}